      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The baseline for a \"global professional\" is to always act with impeccable respect, which means understanding and respecting the cultural norms of the people you are interacting with.  This involves being mindful of local customs regarding dress, greetings, and social interactions, rather than assuming a single standard applies everywhere.  Furthermore, maintaining a high level of discretion and professionalism in all communications is paramount for any high-end brand.",
