    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "makes sense. so if we're looking at communication styles too, like how to carry oneself in a high-stakes meeting—what's the gold standard for being \"polished\"? and if someone is using a more communal or indirect way of speaking, how should our clients view that? is it seen as less professional compared to the standard?",
